---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Statecraft Systems</h1>
    <p class="long-form">
      We help founders, executives, and their teams become capable of creating the outcomes they are after and governing what they build.
    </p>
    <div class="rule"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Two Dimensions</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Technical Capacity</h3>
        <p>We make people AI-native by building real tools on real workflows, on their devices, with their challenges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Structural Capacity</h3>
        <p>We help people see the structures they are in, understand why those structures produce the results they produce, and build new ones that advance toward what they want.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Two Engagement Paths</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Individual Track</h3>
        <p>Direct intervention for the leader. Gain personal technical capability and structural clarity before bringing the capacity to the rest of the organization.</p>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <a href="/services" class="production-link">View Individual Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Team Track</h3>
        <p>Systematic implementation across the organization. Establish structural tension, evaluate current reality, and build the tools and practices required to advance.</p>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <a href="/services" class="production-link">View Team Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Results</h2>
    <p class="long-form">
      The work produces specific, factual outcomes. Two examples of targeted intervention:
    </p>
    <ul class="structural-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Skinner Layne:</strong> Introduction to Claude Code led to immediate gains in workflow, followed by team training, product building, and acceleration of fundraising efforts.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Noah (The Meta Father):</strong> Introduction to Claude Code resulted in rebuilding the entire business platform, moving off Kajabi, and gaining sovereign control over the infrastructure.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section">
    <h2>The Web of Relationships</h2>
    <p class="long-form">
      Working with Statecraft Systems is entry into a web of relationships governed by reciprocity. The web includes Modern Minuteman, The Field Company, independent productions, and tools built for our own use and shared with the network.
    </p>
    <a href="/work" class="production-link">View our Work & Productions</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
